Kroger Shopping List Creator
Returns a shopping list with prices (if available from Kroger API) based on selected store and selected items.

Installation
Python requried

RUN: pip install -r requirements.txt

This command installs requirements such as flask and dotenv

Node.js requried: nvm install --lts (bash) OR nvm install lts (powershell)

Backend server setup: Run two terminals: Flask and Vite

  Python app.py
  cd kroger-calculator
  npm run dev
Deployment
when "http://localhost:5173" is returned, open link to access the app
